## 1. Executive Summary

This specification defines the implementation of a centralized telemetry pipeline that collects, aggregates, and exports performance metrics from all VJLive3 subsystems. It provides real-time monitoring capabilities for the UI, historical data for debugging, and production-grade observability for deployment.

**Critical Objectives:**
- Collect per-plugin execution times with <0.1ms overhead
- Track system metrics (FPS, memory, GPU usage, safety violations)
- Provide real-time data to UI via WebSocket
- Support historical logging and analysis
- Maintain 60 FPS sacred rail under all conditions
- Enable performance regression detection

