## 7. Production Considerations

### 7.1 Performance Impact

- **Recording**: ~0.05ms per call (fast path)
- **Snapshot**: ~0.5ms for 100 metrics (called 1-4 times per second)
- **WebSocket broadcast**: ~0.2ms per second (async)
- **Total overhead**: <1% of 60 FPS budget

### 7.2 Storage

- **Log size**: ~1KB per frame (60 FPS → 3.6MB/min → 216MB/hour)
- **Rotation**: Daily or 100MB
- **Retention**: 7 days (configurable)
- **Compression**: gzip old logs

### 7.3 Security

- Telemetry may contain sensitive data (plugin names, timing patterns)
- Ensure no PII or content data is logged
- Provide opt-out via `VJ_TELEMETRY_ENABLED=0`

