## 9. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Telemetry overhead exceeds budget | High | Benchmark; optimize hot paths; use Cython; reduce frequency |
| Memory leak in metric storage | High | Use deque with maxlen; weak references; monitor growth |
| WebSocket blocks main thread | Medium | Use async broadcast; separate thread |
| Log files consume too much disk | Medium | Aggressive rotation; compression; retention policy |
| Alert spam | Medium | Rate limiting; debouncing; severity levels |
| Sensitive data leaked in logs | High | Sanitize metric names; no content data; opt-out flag |

